function Ndanh() {
    return ( <
        div className = "slide_picture" >
        <
        div className = "chuyen-slide" >
        <
        div className = "slide-tintuc" >
        <
        a href = "true" >
        <
        img src = "img/anhtin1.png"
        alt = "true" / >
        <
        /a> <
        /div> <
        div className = "slide-tintuc" >
        <
        a href = "true" >
        <
        img src = "img/anhtin1.png"
        alt = "true" / >
        <
        /a> <
        /div> <
        div classname = "slide-tintuc" >
        <
        a href = "true" >
        <
        img src = "img/anhtin1.png"
        alt = "true" / >
        <
        /a> <
        /div> <
        /div> <
        p className = "prev"
        onclick = "Back(0)" > ❮
        <
        /p> <
        p className = "next"
        onclick = "Next(0)" > ❯
        <
        /p> <
        /div>

    );
}
export default Ndanh;
